{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2427870/extras/gui_promos_headers_02.png?t=1733921653\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this Tower Defense, you assume the role of a great Gamblemancer. However, The King got words of your incredible gambling prowess, and has decided to put an end to your luck.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is of course non ideal from your perspective. Thus, equip yourself with all kinds of spells and effects to fend off the King's men and goons. Will Lady Luck be on your side?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">[gif to show end game action]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2427870/extras/gui_promos_headers_03.png?t=1733921653\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Spells and effects are highly dice dependant. This means in order to trigger their effects or skills, a roll requirement must first be fulfilled. So it is paramount to your survival that you equip not only powerful spells but also effects that has good trigger conditions. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">[gif to show shop interaction, and roll trigger results]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Should you find yourself in need of extra resources, there will be various mini games in which you can barter and wage your hard earned resources to gain (or lose :) ) the upper hand.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">[gif to show gamba mini games]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2427870/extras/gui_promos_headers_end.png?t=1733921653\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2427870/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733921653","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steam